creator: UnizPortal
descriptionHtml:
UnizPortal connects the world’s institutions, recruiters, students & service providers and empowering them by providing tools, expertise, support to optimise their operations.

Using the UnizPortal Platform, students and recruitment partners can easily search and apply to 1,000+ educational institutions and 30,000+ programs.
